@page "/donation"
@inject NavigationManager Navigation

<div class="page-wrapper">
    <header>
        <h2>Support the Project</h2>
        <p class="header-subtitle">Help keep this tool free and open source</p>
    </header>

    <div class="donation-container">
        <div class="donation-content">
            <div class="nav-link">
                <a href="/" @onclick="@(() => Navigation.NavigateTo("/"))">← Back to RCWA Sweep</a>
            </div>

            <div class="author-section">
                <h3>About the Author</h3>
                <p>
                    The RCWA Sweep Tool was created to provide optical engineers and researchers with 
                    a free, accessible solution for holographic grating design and analysis. This tool 
                    combines rigorous coupled-wave analysis (RCWA) with practical design workflows to 
                    help you optimize your optical systems.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Development of this tool represents hundreds of hours of research, coding, testing, 
                    and refinement. By keeping it free and open source, I hope to contribute to the 
                    optical engineering community and make advanced simulation tools accessible to everyone.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="donation-section">
                <h3>Support Development</h3>
                <p>
                    If you find this tool valuable for your work or research, please consider showing your
                    appreciation. This development is a labor of love. No donations are needed to keep this
                    tool around and free. However, if you would like to contribute, you have my thanks!
                </p>

                <div class="venmo-section">
                    <h4>Donate via Venmo</h4>
                    <p class="venmo-handle"><strong>@@R_Rallison</strong></p>
                    
                    <div class="qr-code-container">
                        <img src="/images/venmo-qr.png" alt="Venmo QR Code - @@R_Rallison" class="qr-code" />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="thank-you">
                    <p>
                        ❤️ <strong>Thank you for your support!</strong> I hope you find this tool helpful or the source
                        code a good starting point for your own projects.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="features-section">
                <h3>How is your donation used?</h3>
                <p>
                    I can promise you one thing. Any donations made to me through Venmo will be spent doing something creative or innovative. I have
                    a wood shop. I love to build things. Maybe your donation will go towards my next piece of custom furnature. I can't tell you precicly
                    how it will be spent, but I gaurantee it will be something fun, helpful, interesting, and made with my own two hands. And you will
                    have my thanks for helping me to continue to do the things that bring me joy.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="open-source-section">
                <h3>Open Source</h3>
                <p>
                    This tool is completely open source and available on GitHub. Feel free to contribute, 
                    report issues, or fork the project for your own needs.
                </p>
                <p>
                    <a href="https://github.com/bertinc/rcwa_sweep_tool" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="github-link">
                        🔗 View on GitHub
                    </a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>RCWA Sweep Tool v@(Constants.Version) - Free and Open Source</p>
    </footer>
</div>
